{"tid":2262841,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"點解among us到依家都咁多人玩?","createTime":"2020-10-29T11:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T08:42:38.000Z","uid":204929,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47f75ca2e75f13424b42da7d395311780778204f","tid":2262841,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CKYyrBD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCKYyrBD.png&h=c40dfe3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明來來去去都係做同一樣嘢!<br />\n嚟嚟去去都係同一個任務!<br />\n<br />\n如果有多少少唔同職業都好啲,但係依家只有做任務同殺手呢兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n原則上應該好快玩厭, 但係點解過咗幾個月都咁多人玩?"},{"pid":"ae88c60e972f364f2c289673cb5e5d73d99e2490","tid":2262841,"uid":245909,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"樓主冇朋友"},{"pid":"28d8d986511ee090bc252395c3209dc03a763b18","tid":2262841,"uid":201414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚搵到唔人玩 所以咪覺得唔好玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7492ec9236d41650976601cf8be8b5782528dd1","tid":2262841,"uid":204929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"28d8d986511ee090bc252395c3209dc03a763b18","tid":2262841,"uid":201414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚搵到唔人玩 所以咪覺得唔好玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"重點係嚟嚟去去都係玩過啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n如果一齊玩可以玩其他㗎"},{"pid":"5178002503b85bc827607817e1649867a32f6f4f","tid":2262841,"uid":76609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"原則上，即係你冇玩過冇人同你玩"},{"pid":"040d5b1e2bff42d3771552ed5b7cf15dd79393a3","tid":2262841,"uid":275055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20